metDecl.p:
10ababc’c’b (MW 1159,1 = Frank 361); 5 coblas doblas (2+2+1) with
          a 3-line envoi (c’c’b); rhyme a = -a, -er, -ez; rhyme b = -is, -ont, -oir; rhyme c = -ance, -ie, -ee;
          identica; rhyme mont in vv. 16 and 22; feminine caesura with
          elision in vv. 2 and 11; lyric caesura in vv. 29 and 36; melody in KMtNOVX, with very few variants (van der Werf 1979, II, p. 3;
          Tischler 1997, I n° 5).
